			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "SiYuan has a built-in CLI (Command Line Interface) that provides direct access to workspace data without starting the kernel server. It is suitable for scripting, batch management, and collaborating with AI agents to read and write note data."
				}
			]
		},
